								<div class="term-badges floated"><span class="term-badge term-497"><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210224235429/https://globalsecurityreview.com/economics-trade/">Economics &amp; Trade</a></span></div>									<h1 class="single-post-title">
										<span class="post-title" itemprop="headline">Russian Influence in Mongolia is Declining</span></h1>
																		<div class="post-meta-wrap clearfix">
										<div class="post-meta single-post-meta">
