				<a title="Transnistria: No Longer an Illegal Trade Hub?" data-src="https://mk0globalsecuridd2hf.kinstacdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/31437310490_fffc2390eb_k-86x64.jpg" data-bs-srcset="{&quot;baseurl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/globalsecurityreview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/&quot;,&quot;sizes&quot;:{&quot;86&quot;:&quot;31437310490_fffc2390eb_k-86x64.jpg&quot;,&quot;210&quot;:&quot;31437310490_fffc2390eb_k-210x136.jpg&quot;,&quot;2048&quot;:&quot;31437310490_fffc2390eb_k.jpg&quot;}}" class="img-holder" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210224235429/https://globalsecurityreview.com/transnistria-no-longer-illegal-trade-hub/"></a>
